title: Euro Truck Simulator 2 Patch + Crack V1.4.12
description:
Version 1.4.12 patch and crack update for ETS 2.

This update improves some features of the game.


    *Improved resistance to some of the mod conflicts.
    *Added prefabs replace command simplifying rename of prefabs.
    *Fixed issues with advisor after teleporting.
    *Fixed several possible instabilities.
    *Fixed positioning of some company trailers.
    *Fixed bug glitches.
